lead_paragraph: The anticipation's been building and it's finally time — Week 1 of the 2016 fantasy football season is here. Our first tip: Relax and don't let the hype of the NFL opener Thursday between the Panthers and the Broncos get you too high or low on your team.

headline.print_headline: FANTASY PLAYS: A Primer for Week 1 (and Rest of the Season)
